   <concept id="FAR_47_404" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">47.404</ph> Air freight forwarders.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d2810e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2837e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Agencies may use air freight forwarders that are engaged in international air transportation (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title49-section1301(c)&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">49 U.S.C. 1301(c)</xref>) for U.S. Government-financed movements of property. The rule on disallowance of expenditures in <xref href="47.403-3.dita#FAR_47_403_3"
                        base="i1070013"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">47.403-3</xref>(a) applies also to the air carriers used by these international air freight forwarders.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2837e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Agency personnel shall inform international air freight forwarders that to facilitate prompt payments of their bills, they shall submit with their bills-</p>
               <ol id="d2810e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2837e27">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                A copy of the airway bill or manifest showing the air carriers used; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d2837e32">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Justification for the use of foreign-flag air carriers similar to the one shown in the clause at <xref href="52.247-63.dita#FAR_52_247_63"
                              base="i1046532"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.247-63</xref>, Preference for U.S.-Flag Air Carriers.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
